      "content": "Your body's metabolism is unpredictable, and cutting warfarin to 2mg without monitoring your INR could easily lead to a dangerous clot or a fatal bleed. Even if your lifestyle is perfect, factors like diet, supplements, or minor illnesses can drastically change how your body processes the drug. Please do not adjust your dose on your own; your safety depends on keeping the medication exactly as prescribed until a professional reviews your labs.",
      "source": "target",
